DESCRIPTION {
    Coincidence or chaos in the personnel files? Which animals are called the same as one or more employees?
    
    List them sorted in descending order according to the employee's surname.
}

ANSWER {
    SELECT name, type, firstname, surname
    FROM zoo_animal 
    JOIN zoo_employee ON zoo_employee.firstname = zoo_animal.name 
    ORDER BY surname ASC;
}

